1. Ona *odvede* psa u šetnju. (She took the dog for a walk.)
2. Prošlog leta sam *odveo* svoju porodicu na more. (Last summer I took my family to the seaside.)
3. Policija ga je *odvela* u stanicu radi ispitivanja. (The police took him to the station for questioning.)
4. Nisam znao da će me toliko *odvesti* moja nova poslovna prilika. (I didn't know that my new business opportunity would take me that far.)
5. Kada sam *odveo* svoj automobil na popravak, otkrili su da je problem veći nego što sam mislio. (When I took my car for repair, they discovered that the problem was bigger than I thought.)
6. Nikada ne znaš kuda će te život *odvesti*. (You never know where life will take you.)
7. On je *odveden* u bolnicu zbog povrede kolena. (He was taken to the hospital due to a knee injury.)
8. Da li bi mogao da *odvezeš* ove kutije do magacina? (Could you take these boxes to the warehouse?)
9. Ona je *odvodila* svoju decu u školu svakog jutra. (She used to take her children to school every morning.)
10. Kada se *odvozim* do posla, uvek slušam omiljenu muziku. (When I drive to work, I always listen to my favorite music.)